<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>Bách hóa ngọc minh</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/custom-bootstrap.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/canvas.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.css">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.7.0/css/all.css'>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/sweetalert.css">

</head>

<body class="home">
    <div class="wrapper overlay">   
        <header id="header">
            <div class="header-wrapper">
                <div class="header-main">
                    <div class="container">
                        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light ">
                            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                                data-target="#navbarTogglerDemo01" aria-controls="navbarTogglerDemo01"
                                aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                            </button>
                            <div class="navbar-header">
                                <a class="navbar-brand" href="#"> <img width="270px" height="84px"
                                        src="uploads/logo1.jpg" alt=""></a>

                            </div>
                            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarTogglerDemo01">
                            </div>
                            <ul class="navbar-nav mt-2 mt-lg-0 m-0" style="float: right;">
                                <li class="btn-cart-item-header active-nav-bar">
                                    <span class="Price-amount"></span><i class="fas fa-shopping-cart" data-cart-icon="0"></i>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </nav>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </header>
        <main class="main">

            </section>
            <section class="section product-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="bg section-bg fill bg-fill  bg-loaded"></div>
                    <div class="product">
                        <div class="product-inner">
                            <div id="listsanpham" class="row justify-content-center" style="margin-top: 10px;">
                                
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <input type="text" style="display: none;" id="magiamgiasave"></input>
        <input type="text" style="display: none;" id="tongtiensaugiamgia"></input>
        <footer class="footer">
            <div class="footer-wrapper">
                <section class="section footer-section">
                    <div class="section-bg ">

                    </div>
                    <div class="footer-content">
                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-4">
                                    <h3>Về chúng tôi</h3>
                                    <span>Chúng tôi tự hào là nhà cung cấp Mật ong hàng đầu tại Việt Nam, với hơn 10 năm
                                        kinh nghiệm cung cấp mật ong cho thị trường Việt Nam, cũng như xuất khẩu.</span>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </footer>

    </div>
    <div id="cart-popup" class="widget_shopping_cart ">
        <div class="close-sidebar">
            <button id="btn-close" class="btn-close ">X</button>
        </div>

        <div class="cart-popup-inner inner-padding">
            <div class="cart-popup-title text-center">
                <h4 class="uppercase">Giỏ hàng</h4>
                <div class="is-divider"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="cart-sidebar-content">
                <div class="row p-0 m-0">
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <ul id="cart-list" class="cart-list product-list-item">
                        </ul>
                        </br>
                        <center><strong>Mã Giảm Giá</strong></center>
                        <table style="width: 100%">
                            <tr>
                                <td width="80%"><input type="text" style="display: inline;" class="form-control" id="magiamgia"></td>
                                <td width="20%"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="Apdungmagiamgia()">Áp dụng</button></td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                        
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                
                
            </div>
            <div class="cart-total">
                <strong>Tạm tính:</strong>
                <span class="Price-amount"></span>
                <span class="Price-currencySymbol"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="cart-buttons">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-dark" onclick="thanhtoan()">Thanh toán</button>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal fade" id="ThanhToan" role="dialog">
                <div class="modal-dialog">
                
                  <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header" style="background-color:#e8e9ea">
                      <h4 class="modal-title">Thanh Toán</h4>
                      <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>    
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                  <div>

                    <label> Họ Và Tên:<span style="color: red">*</span> </label>
                    <span id="yeucauhoten" style="color: red"></span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" rows="3" id="hoten" style="resize: none"></input>
                    <label> Số Điện Thoại:<span style="color: red">*</span> </label>
                    <span id="yeucausdt" style="color: red"></span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" rows="3" id="sdt" style="resize: none"></input>
                    <label> Địa Chỉ:<span style="color: red">*</span> </label>
                    <span id="yeucaudiachi" style="color: red"></span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" rows="3" id="diachi" style="resize: none"></input>
                    <label> Email:<span style="color: red">*</span> </label>
                    <span id="yeucauemail" style="color: red"></span>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" rows="3" id="email" style="resize: none"></input>
                    <label> Ghi Chú: </label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" rows="3" id="ghichu" style="resize: none"></input>
                  </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                      <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Đóng</button>
                  <button type="button" class="btn btn-success" onclick="DatHang()">Lưu</button>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
            </div>
</body>
